      "message": "PTAL\n\nThe Token Server hits this when it calls SignBytes from inside a request handler. SignBytes implementation uses GetRPCTransport(AsSelf) created during the server startup. So we end up using such \"background\" transport from within a request handler that has some non-trivial auth context.\n\nI\u0027m not sure why we hit it only now. I suspect other libraries we use (Spanner, Cloud datastore) do not propagate context.Context all the way from public API calls (like datastore.Get) down to the HTTP request level.",
